question:
District category contains Dormitory District, Gated Community, Capitol District, and Cultural Heritage Site.
Supermarkets category contains Stop & Shop, Shipt, and King Soopers.
Product category contains Canned Beans, Canned Coconut Milk, and Cottage Cheese.
Ingredient category contains Paprika, Dried Fruit, and Dill.
The number of each King Soopers 's Canned Beans equals each Gated Community 's Stop & Shop.
The number of each Shipt 's Cottage Cheese equals 15 more than each Stop & Shop 's Cottage Cheese.
The number of each Gated Community 's Stop & Shop equals 15.
The number of each Dormitory District 's King Soopers equals 0.
The number of each Canned Beans 's Paprika equals 13.
The number of each Stop & Shop 's Cottage Cheese equals the sum of each Cottage Cheese 's Dried Fruit, each Cottage Cheese 's Ingredient, each Dormitory District 's King Soopers, and each Dormitory District 's Supermarkets.
The number of each Canned Coconut Milk 's Dried Fruit equals 6.
The number of each Capitol District 's King Soopers equals 7.
The number of each Canned Coconut Milk 's Paprika equals 1 more than the sum of each Shipt 's Ingredient and each Gated Community 's Stop & Shop.
The number of each Cultural Heritage Site 's Shipt equals 19 times each Stop & Shop 's Ingredient.
The number of each Cottage Cheese 's Dried Fruit equals the sum of each Dormitory District 's Supermarkets and each Dormitory District 's King Soopers.
How many Ingredient does Cultural Heritage Site have?
solution:
Define each Dormitory District 's King Soopers as a; So a = 0.
Define each Dormitory District 's Supermarkets as z; So z = a = 0.
Define each Cottage Cheese 's Dried Fruit as G; So G = z + a = 0 + 0 = 0.
Define each Cottage Cheese 's Ingredient as I; So I = G = 0.
Define each Stop & Shop 's Cottage Cheese as E; B = I + a = 0 + 0 = 0; T = B + z = 0 + 0 = 0; So E = G + T = 0 + 0 = 0.
Define each Stop & Shop 's Ingredient as f; f = I * E = 0 * 0 = 0.
Define each Shipt 's Cottage Cheese as P; So P = 15 + E = 15 + 0 = 15.
Define each Cultural Heritage Site 's Shipt as V; So V = 19 * f = 19 * 0 = 0.
Define each Shipt 's Ingredient as b; b = P * I = 15 * 0 = 0.
Define each Cultural Heritage Site 's Ingredient as s; s = b * V = 0 * 0 = 0.
